      "page": 1,
      "title": "How Can Families Get Free Tablets",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How Can Families Get Free Tablets</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<p>Cellular companies now provide free phones or tablets to low-income families, aiding communication and essential resource access. These devices are offered through the Lifeline assistance program, benefiting families on government assistance like SNAP food stamps or EBT cards.</p>\n<img alt=\"How Can Families Get Free Tablets_1\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-can-families-get-free-tablets/how-can-families-get-free-tablets_1.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-can-families-get-free-tablets/how-can-families-get-free-tablets_1.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-can-families-get-free-tablets/how-can-families-get-free-tablets_1.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-can-families-get-free-tablets/how-can-families-get-free-tablets_1.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 2,
      "title": "How Can Families Get Free Tablets",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>How Can Families Get Free Tablets</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>1. EBT Users Get Tablets From Cellular Companies</h4>\n<img alt=\"How Can Families Get Free Tablets_2\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-can-families-get-free-tablets/how-can-families-get-free-tablets_2.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-can-families-get-free-tablets/how-can-families-get-free-tablets_2.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/how-can-families-get-free-tablets/how-can-families-get-free-tablets_2.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/how-can-families-get-free-tablets/how-can-families-get-free-tablets_2.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Food stamps, also known as SNAP, provide food assistance for low-income individuals. They offer cash-like benefits and nutrition education programs. Furthermore, some programs now offer technology assistance, including free phones or tablets from phone companies, to eligible recipients.</p>\n</img></div>"
    },
